message.content:
Tēnā koe! Kei te whakararuraru ahau ki ēnei āwhina. Me whakapau kaha ahau ki te whakamahi i te reo Māori ki te whakamārama i ngā whakamahi whakaeke ipurangi. Tīmata tātou!

1. Ka whakarite koe i tō pouako īmēra. Kia whakapau kaha koe ki te whakapā mai ki a rātou ki te whakamōhio i tō hiahia ki te whakaeke ipurangi. Ka whakapau kaha hoki koe ki te ako i ngā kupu whakarite e whai pānga ana ki tō hiahia.

2. Kia whakapau kaha koe ki te rapu i tētahi āwhina whakaeke ipurangi mō tō hiahia. Ka whakarite koe i tōku whakararuraru i te tīpakonga o te whakaeke ipurangi, ā, ka rapu i te wāhanga āwhina, pūrongo, tūtohu, whārangi tautoko, rānei. Kia kaha koe ki te whakamārama i ngā whakamahi i ngā āhuatanga o te whakaeke ipurangi i runga i te āwhina.

3. Me whakapau kaha koe ki te ako i ngā whakamahi tino hōhonu o te whakaeke ipurangi. Ka whakarite koe i ētahi pātai whakamārama e whai pānga ana ki tō hiahia. Ka whakapau kaha koe ki te rangahau i ētahi āwhina, video, rauemi whakamārama, rānei, e whakamārama ana i ngā tikanga whakaeke i runga i te whakaeke ipurangi.

4. Me whakapau kaha koe ki te whakatika
